snippet.title: Praesidium Update Trailer
snippet.description:
Available now on Steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1570720/Praesidium/

Praesidium has been updated with new environments and menu settings, along with a new tutorial level to teach you game features.

Praesidium is a fast-paced, speedrunner, single player experience in a futuristic setting. Run and jump across city rooftops, while dodging incoming turret fire and launching yourself into the air with your high-tech shield.
